title: your account is in the process of transferring regions
body: I have an account thunderdragon8 and I changed regions from NA to EUNE and it's not letting me in. I was hoping a riot worker can tell me if my account was changed correctly.

replies.body: I looked into this for you, but it looks like your account was already transferred.  is this still an issue?  Keep in mind that if you were on EUNE previously, you may have to use that older username.
ya but idk what my old username is...  ya it's still a problem idk its not letting me login and I've never been on EUNE
